  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个TCP包结构图，用于给金融科技团队讲解底层协议。重点是展示标准头部字段，但要在Options和Data区域标注我们内部的服务标识。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "packet-beta",
        "Source Port",
        "Destination Port",
        "Options",
        "Data"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。标准TCP头部是32位一行，总共至少5行（160位）的固定头部。您说的服务标识是指Options字段放FinTech_FraudDetection，Data字段放FinTech_LedgerService吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Options",
        "Data",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection",
        "FinTech_LedgerService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是那个对应关系。另外控制位区域要清晰标出URG、ACK、PSH、RST、SYN、FIN这六个标志位，特别是ACK和URG要突出显示。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "URG",
        "ACK",
        "PSH",
        "RST",
        "SYN",
        "FIN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出基础结构：0-15位是Source Port，16-31位是Destination Port，然后32-63放Sequence Number，64-95是Acknowledgment Number。控制位从106位开始，URG在106，ACK在107，依次排到111位的FIN。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Source Port",
        "Destination Port",
        "Sequence Number",
        "Acknowledgment Number",
        "Data Offset",
        "Reserved"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "等等，控制位后面紧跟着Window字段对吧？还有Checksum和Urgent Pointer也要标清楚位宽。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Window",
        "Checksum",
        "Urgent Pointer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：112-127是Window（16位），128-143是Checksum（16位），144-159是Urgent Pointer（16位）。这样固定头部正好160位，之后160-191是Options，192-255是Data。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Window",
        "Checksum",
        "Urgent Pointer",
        "Options",
        "Data"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "Options的位宽不对，160-191是32位，但标准TCP Options是可变长的。不过我们这次就用32位示意，标注成FinTech_FraudDetection。Data区域192-255是64位，标注FinTech_LedgerService。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Options",
        "Data",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection",
        "FinTech_LedgerService"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整完成。整个包结构现在包含：标题\"Estructura del paquete TCP\"，从Source Port到Destination Port的端口号，完整的Sequence和Acknowledgment编号，6个控制标志位（URG/ACK/PSH/RST/SYN/FIN），Window大小、Checksum校验、Urgent Pointer紧急指针，以及最后两个标注了金融科技服务的Options和Data字段。",
